1.27
log
@word fix; from henning petersen (netbsd pr/49641, -r1.18)
ok millert
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: gethostname.3,v 1.26 2015/01/12 10:11:07 nicm Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1983, 1991, 1993
.\"	The Regents of the University of California.  All rights reserved.
